{"tid":1666243,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「港城PRG」魔王店最怕咩？","createTime":"2019-10-21T02:02:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T02:02:03.000Z","uid":312758,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"58fa07f6e8624c6f08daa9a0aac8c2beb5d8d40b","tid":1666243,"uid":312758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T02:02:03.000Z","msg":"火魔法攻擊力最強，但係難控制又麻煩到救火英雄。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n水魔法範圍最大，但係水源少。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n土木魔法時效最長，鎖上鎖，牆外牆，理論上可行，未實踐。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n召喚術威嚇力最高，但係收集召喚物有一定危險性。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n物理攻擊最簡單，穿透性不足。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}